title: Ephemera, "Album: Maison Mendessalle"
description: The company name, Maison Mendessalle, is imprinted on coated black paper in white in a hand-lettered style upright script, in which the height of the capital "M" and letter "l" are exaggerated.

Ephemera, "Album: Maison Mendessalle".
8.4 x 27 cm (3 1/4 x 10 3/4 in.). Gift of Ellen Gustav Jensen. 1956-47-84-jj.
